prehensive and include a real subprocess round-trip check.\n\n## Issues Found\n- None.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe implementation is solid and the verification tests confirm the security properties required by DAB-071.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-002@20260530t002730z-verify.md"}}
